¡Crocodile!

7
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:59,450
¡Crocodile!

8
00:08:45,130 --> 00:08:47,590
¡Eres maravillosa, Nami-san!

9
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,720
¡No tenemos!

10
00:11:59,740 --> 00:12:02,580
Mola

11
00:11:59,740 --> 00:12:02,580
Shi

12
